RoomTemplate.Description: This room is for mobs that get lost or are taken out of play for some reason.

RoomTemplate.Title: &+mA Boring Purple Room Called '&+GLimbo&n&+m'&n
RoomTemplate.Description: &+m This room is for silly mortals, like yourself, who don't have a player home yet. We'll have a place for you someday, I swear. To the south lies an exit, this will toss you into the Testport connector. This currently connects all of the zones for testing purposes. &+m If you find a bug, a typo, and just plain get a spiffy idea, let us know all about it. We love to hear from ya. The command is <typo> <note> or <bug> <note>, etc. Also check the news, we are changing daily!
